</A><br>
<DT><IMG SRC="/Images/redball.gif" ALT= "o"><A HREF="#subj4">
  Disk space cleanup causes problems with on-line Bar Admission exam     
</A>
<DD>
<A HREF="#subj4.1">
David Sherman
