<DT><IMG SRC="/Images/redball.gif" ALT= "o"><A HREF="#subj5">
  Re: Altitude encoders: $1500 for Mode C?  No, $750. 
</A>
<DD>
<A HREF="#subj5.1">
Jordan Brown
