<DT><IMG SRC="/Images/redball.gif" ALT= "o"><A HREF="#subj3">
  Ex-Directory [Arrested by unwristed phone mumbers!] 
</A>
<DD>
<A HREF="#subj3.1">
Brian Randell
</A><br>
<DT><IMG SRC="/Images/redball.gif" ALT= "o"><A HREF="#subj4">
  Risks of Computerized Airport Gate Signs 
</A>
<DD>
<A HREF="#subj4.1">
