<H3><A NAME="subj10.1">
Re: Risks of so-called ``computer addiction''
</A>
</H3>
<address>
John Mackin
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:munnari!basser.cs.su.oz!john@seismo.CSS.GOV ">
munnari!basser.cs.su.oz!john@seismo.CSS.GOV 
</A>&gt;
</address>
<i>
16 Jun 87 18:09:47 GMT
</i><PRE>
