In response to an article in:
RISKS-LIST: RISKS-FORUM Digest  Wenesday, 30 Sept 1987  Volume 5 : Issue 41
&gt;From: P. T. Withington &lt;PTW@YUKON.SCRC.Symbolics.COM&gt;
